  "bookTitle": "Succubus Songstress",
  "bookId": 70,
  "firstAcquaintance": "Yasena's childhood friend and the standout among the new generation of succubi. Her tenderness can conquer anyone.",
  "personality": "She doesn't like to show off, but always holds the upper hand. She can be quite severe at times, and when she is, you'd better watch out.",
  "like": "Yasena, bubble tea",
  "familiarData": "In truth, she's a sharp-tongued woman. What outsiders see as a nurse's uniform is actually her succubus work attire, primarily used for handling farm duties.\nShe inherited succubus abilities and applies them in combat and every aspect of daily life. She may not look like a typical succubus, but she constantly deploys succubus techniques with perfect control, earning her the title of 'the perfect succubus.'\n\nShe and Yasena are childhood friends of similar age. In fact, that's exactly why 'Mother' brought her into the world, to serve Yasena. Though her life was a prearranged plan, she doesn't resent it at all. She genuinely feels that being Yasena's friend is an incredibly joyful thing, and has sworn loyalty to Yasena in her heart, aspiring to support her as the future Succubus Queen.\nHer signature ability is 'Energy Storage,' allowing her to store excess magic power or absorbed life force in her womb. At full capacity, she can hold three times her normal amount. The stored power can't be released directly, so she doesn't have three times the combat strength. However, she compensates with the ability to fight continuously and her rare gift of energy transfer. In that regard, she truly is like a nurse.",
